title: Transferring Account
body:
Hi may I know if it's still possible to transfer my account from Garena SEA to OCE server? 

Thanks.

replies.body:
SephirothSG is correct.
It was a technical nightmare that transfer and there were not many players affected so we no longer provide that service.

Hey there,

From what I can gather it seems that transfers from Garena -> OCE are no longer possible, please see [this](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/garena-oceania-transfers-faq) page for more information, specifically [this](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/garena-oceania-transfers-faq#process5) question.

>**How long will transfer registrations be available?**
Registration for Garena to Oceania account transfers will be available from December 5, 2013 until December 18, 2013.
